                <msItem xml:id="ms_i4.6">
                 <locus from="130rb" to="131vb"/>
                 <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1694Jonah">Book of Jonah</title>
             <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">
               ወኮነ፡ ቃለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ኀበ፡ ዮናስ፡ ነቢይ፡ ወልደ፡</hi> አማቴ፡ ወይቤሎ፡ ተንሥእ፡ ወሑር፡
