    <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
     <locus from="201rb" to="203rc"/>
      <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4089Introduction">A chronology of Biblical and Ethiopian kings attributed to Giyorgis Walda ʾAmid</title>
  <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡
    ፩፡ አምላክ፡ በስ</hi>መ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መሐሪ፡ ወመተሣህል፡ ንዌጥን፡ ጽሒፈ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘይነግር፡
    ኍልቈ፡ ዓመታተ፡ ዓለም፡ ዘአስተጋብኦ፡ አብ፡ ክቡር፡ ወትሩፍ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወልደ፡ አሚድ፡ ዘብሔረ፡ ግብጽ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
    ይቤ፡ እስመ፡ ሠራዕያነ፡ ሕግሰ፡ ይቤሉ፡ እምኍልቈ፡ ዓመታተ፡ ኮነ፡ እምጥንቱ፡ እስከ፡ ተፍጻሜቱ፡ ፸፻ዓመት፡ አልቦ፡ ዘየአምሮ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ እመጻሕፍቲሆሙ፡ 
    ወመምህራንሰ፡ ጻመዉ፡ ወጽሕቁ፡ በአርትዖ፡ ታሪኮሙ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ሐሳባቲሆሙ፡ ወዘተጠየቀ፡ በኀቤሆሙ፡ ከመ፡ ኮነ፡ እምአመ፡ ተፈጥረ፡ አዳም፡ 
    እስከ፡ አመ፡ አስተርአየ፡ ክርስቶስ፡
  </incipit>
      <note>The part on the Biblical kings is shortened and
      the chronology of the Ethiopian kings extended up to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9449Tewoflos">King Tewoflos</persName>
     (reigned in <date>1708-11</date>). The witness was not used in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/EFE2TAZF"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Kropp2016Zekra"/><title level="m">Zekra Nagar. Die universalhistorische Einleitung nach Giyorgis Walda-Amid in der Chronikensammlung des Haylu</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Manfred</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kropp</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Speyer</pubPlace><publisher>Kartoffeldruck-Verlag Kai Brodersen</publisher><date>2016</date></bibl>.
                
    </note>
  </msItem>
