                                 <q xml:lang="gez">ኍልቈ፡ እህል፡ ዘወጽአ፡ በዘመነ፡ ሉቃስ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="DN"/></q>

                                 <note>The note concerns tributes or a transaction with cereals; 
                                   it has been edited in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/MZC4PZ7D"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1914Notice"/><title level="m">Notice sur les manuscrits éthiopiens de la Collection d’Abbadie</title><title level="s">Extrait du Journal Asiatique</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Carlo</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Conti Rossini</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Imprimerie nationale</publisher><date>1914</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Extrait du Journal Asiatique</t:title></series><citedRange unit="page">40</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                  </item>

                                  <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus from="1r" to="2r"/>

                                     <desc type="GuestText"><title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2872RepCh153">Malkǝʾa ʾarbāʿtu ʾǝnsǝsā</title>Malkǝʾ-hymn for the 
                                       Four Living Creatures.</desc>
                                     </item>

                                     <item xml:id="a3">
                                       <locus target="#3r"/>
                                        <desc type="OwnershipNote"/>
                                       <q xml:lang="gez">ይትባርክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አምላከ፡ እስራኤል፡ ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ለአባ፡ አሕዋን፡</q>
                                           <note>The note is written in a crude hand, in the upper margin,
                                             in two columns. It mentions the owner,
                                             a <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/ETH1274Betaes">Beta ʾƎsrāʾel</persName> man <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12914Ahwan">
                                             ʾabbā ʾAḥwān</persName> from whom
                                             <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1071dAbbadi">Antoine d'Abbadie</persName>
                                             bought the manuscript. The number 30 could have been added later.</note>
                                         </item>

                                         <item xml:id="a4">
                                           <locus from="202va" to="203ra"/>
                                           <desc type="Unclear">A historiographical note featuring the chronology 
                                             from the reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10473Yostos">King Yosṭos</persName>
                                             (r. <date>1711-16</date>) up to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9152TaklaHa">King Takla Hāymānot</persName>;
                                             it stops on events from ca. <date>1772</date></desc>

                                           <q xml:lang="gez"><persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10473Yostos">ዮስጦስ፡</persName> ፬፡ዓ፡ ከ፡ ፭፡ አው፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                             ወእምድኅረዝ፡ ወረደ፡ <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC6569Tegray">ትግሬ፡</placeName>ምስለ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7091Mikael">ራስ፡ ሚካኤል፡</persName>ወነበረት፡
                                            ምድር፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ፪አውራኃ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9039Susenyos">ሱስንዮስ</persName>፡ ነግሠ፡ ፭አውራኃ፡ ወእምድኅረዝ፡ ኮነ፡ ቀትል፡ ምስለ፡<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7091Mikael">
                                             ሚካኤል፡ </persName>ወነበረት፡ ምድር፡ ዘእንበለ፡
                                                 ንጉሥ፡ ፬አውራኃ፡ ወእምድኅረ፡ ተመውአ፡ ራስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ተመይጠ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9152TaklaHa">
                                                 ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</persName> ወነበረ፡ ዲበ፡ መንበሩ፡ ወነግሠ፡ ወበዳግም፡ ዓመት፡ በዕለተ፡ ትንሣኤ፡ ተእኅዘ፡
                                                 <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9152TaklaHa">ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</persName>
                                                  በእጅ፡<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10025WandBa"><foreign xml:lang="amh">ደጅ፡ አዝማች፡</foreign> ወንድ፡ በወሰን፡</persName>
                                                  ወተፄወወ፡ ወሖረ፡ <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC1713Bagemd">በጌምድር</placeName>። </q>
                                              <note>The note was probably meant to be a continuation of <ref target="#ms_i7"/>.
                                                It has been added later in a different hand. The <foreign xml:lang="am">tamallas</foreign>-sign
                                                 indicates that the note continues on <locus target="#203ra"/>.</note>
                                              </item>

                                              <item xml:id="a5">
                                                <locus target="#202ra"/>
                                                <desc type="DonationNote"/>
                                                <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡  ዝ<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12916MazraetaKrestos">መዝራዕተ፡  ክርስቶስ፡</persName> ወብእሲቱ፡ ምልእተ፡ ጸጋ፡  ወውሉዱ፡ ፡
                                                  ፍስሐ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ስብስትያኖስ፡ አምደ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ዘአጥረዮ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩን፡ ለመድኀኒተ፡ ነፍሱ፡ ዘሰረቆ፡ ፡
                                                  <gap reason="omitted"/>.</q>
                                                <note> The note is written in the main hand.</note>
                                              </item>

                                              <item xml:id="e1">
                                                <desc type="StampExlibris"/>
                                                <note>Shelfmark of the Bibliothèque nationale on the front board, poorly readable,
                                                  and another one the inner side of the board (Ethiop. Abb. 30).</note>
                                                </item>
                            
                            <item xml:id="e2">
                              <locus target="#3r"/>
                              <desc type="StampExlibris"/>
                              <note>Shelfmark of the Bibliothèque nationale (no. 30).</note>
                            </item>

                                    <item xml:id="e3">
                                      <locus target="#47r"/>
                                    <desc>A few rubricated words are added in the main hand, in the upper margin;
                                      possibly omitted from the main text.</desc>
                                  </item>

                                  <item xml:id="e4">
                                    <locus target="#52r #115r'"/>
                                     <desc>A few words are added in the main hand,
                                       possibly omitted from the main text.</desc>
                                   </item>

                                   <item xml:id="e5">
                                     <locus target="#114v #115r"/>
                                      <desc>A few notes in small script on these and
                                        other folios, probably by Antoine d'Abbadie.</desc>
                                    </item>


                          </list>
